+    "en": "<h2>Kiosk Mode</h2><p>Kiosk mode is <strong>enabled</strong> for this Media Server. It is meant to demonstrate the feel of the UI with some data.</p><p>All of the data is pregenerated mock data with no relation to any real music. Any similarities are purely coincidential.</p><p>A few other things are different in kiosk mode:</p><ul><li>Album covers were randomly generated and will change every time you load a page.</li><li>Artist images were sourced randomly from <a href='https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Main_Page' target='_blank'>Wikimedia Commons</a>.</li><li>Most admin features are disabled.</li></ul>",
